overview: A lonely, closeted, Britney Spears fan gets a Spear-itual awakening when he comes across an anonymous support group of Britney-holics.  We follow the journey of Freddie from denial, curiosity, and finally acceptance.
tagline: Freddie gets a Spear-itual awakening when he joins an anonymous support group for closeted Britney Spears fans.
title: Britney-holics Anonymous: A Spear-itual Awakening
